==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fool around with
<hw>fool` a*round" with`</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To manipulate (a
machine or device) without proper knowledge of its operation; to
experiment aimlessly with a device; <as>as, don't <ex>fool around
with</ex> the transit</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fool-born</ent>⟦br⟧
